Enthusiastic, professional facilitators deliver industry focused training in a face-to-face environment. The format provides many opportunities to share experiences and discuss relevant topics with your fellow Frontline Management colleagues. A blended delivery model is used for this program, combining on-the-job and workshop training&lt;br /&gt;
and assessments, and participants will complete their studies via the following activities:&lt;br /&gt;
WS - Workshop attendance (as per course timetable)&lt;br /&gt;
SDL - Self directed learning, i.e. pre-reading requirements; development of project plan, writing of report and presentation (in your own time)&lt;br /&gt;
OTJ ? On the job (activities to undertake at your workplace)

